  "instructions": [
    "heat oil in donabe over medium heat.",
    "add lemongrass, galangal, and chili peppers, saut\u000440 until fragrant.",
    "add yam and plantain, cook until slightly tender.",
    "add coconut milk, miso paste, fish sauce, rice vinegar, and brown sugar, stir to combine.",
    "add water, bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "use slotted spoon to transfer vegetables to serving bowl.",
    "whisk cornstarch and a little water in a small bowl, then stir into stew to thicken, if desired.",
    "season with salt to taste.",
    "serve hot, garnished with kaffir lime leaves, if desired."
